Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{title}Elen
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.79,0:01:36.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Reiji...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.97,0:01:43.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My apologies for arriving late.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.25,0:01:44.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You are...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.94,0:01:46.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Uncle Daisuke's...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.62,0:02:46.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Mom...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.44,0:02:47.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is this about your dad?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.97,0:02:52.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A lot of people mentioned Dad and Uncle Daisuke...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.03,0:02:57.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I knew we'd have to talk about this eventually.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.62,0:03:01.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But that time came sooner than I expected.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.02,0:03:09.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The truth is your father isn't dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.78,0:03:12.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's still alive.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.37,0:03:18.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He lives in an unimaginably cruel world.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.04,0:03:20.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mom...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.49,0:03:22.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...are you okay with that?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.88,0:03:25.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Back then, I wanted us to live together.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.02,0:03:28.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't mind giving up my life for that.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.68,0:03:30.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.87,0:03:33.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm glad things are the way they are.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.83,0:03:37.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,By leaving me behind,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.74,0:03:39.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,he was able to keep his memories of me.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.36,0:03:44.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The only precious thing in our hearts that we can rely on.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.51,0:03:51.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He longed for how we live now.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.46,0:03:54.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But that's something he'll never reach.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.32,0:03:58.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A place that can only be thought of from far far away.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.34,0:04:01.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A place that can only be reached in dreams.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.65,0:04:07.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If I had followed him instead,\Nhis wishes would have been destroyed.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.65,0:04:15.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm living the life that he wanted to live.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.43,0:04:21.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just being together is not real love.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.97,0:04:24.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mom...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.01,0:04:28.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Daisuke was the son of your father and his previous wife.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.31,0:04:34.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He endured everything because he had a little sister who was living the life that he dreamed of.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.14,0:04:36.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's what he told me.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.04,0:04:39.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.10,0:04:45.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I have something to tell him.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.69,0:04:54.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Jeez...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.61,0:04:57.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She definitely has my blood.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.08,0:05:07.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Crap... I can't find them without any clues!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.46,0:05:15.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is this Fujieda?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.51,0:05:18.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, Elen saved me.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.12,0:05:21.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm back home now.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.57,0:05:22.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's great.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.39,0:05:24.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Reiji...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.13,0:05:27.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Elen and Cal are going to kill each other.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.38,0:05:30.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I overheard their phone conversation.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.80,0:05:38.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She said it'll be at some place that they both know at 3am.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.78,0:05:41.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A place that they both know?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.48,0:05:49.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And also... Cal must be in a lot of pain.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.57,0:05:52.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She has no one to talk to.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.41,0:05:56.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Reiji, I'm counting on you to take care of them.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.92,0:05:59.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, don't worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.29,0:06:01.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll definitely do something about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.35,0:06:07.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Fujieda...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.11,0:06:10.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm really sorry about what happened this time.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.98,0:06:13.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's all my fault.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.55,0:06:16.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't say that. I don't mind at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.98,0:06:19.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll forget about it by tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.06,0:06:24.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's why I'll always be here to welcome you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.37,0:06:28.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I love your smiling face.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.62,0:06:35.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you can be that happy, it must mean that this place is right for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.23,0:06:37.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.25,0:06:39.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Really, thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.78,0:06:42.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Fujieda, I-
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.93,0:06:44.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll wait for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.71,0:06:54.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll always wait for the day when you'll return to this city without any worries.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.36,0:06:58.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's why this isn't goodbye.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.99,0:07:00.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please be safe.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.24,0:07:03.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.22,0:07:06.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm off.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.39,0:07:23.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Listen up. Don't go easy on them just because they're kids.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.15,0:07:25.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you going to kill them?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.14,0:07:28.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll be right there.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.10,0:07:34.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've sworn to prevent Mio from getting hurt ever again.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.87,0:07:37.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you think this is what she wants?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.58,0:07:41.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is the one promise I made to Daisuke.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.83,0:07:44.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How selfish.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.58,0:07:46.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You people are always like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.31,0:07:57.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shiga, the one who shot Daisuke was...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.05,0:08:22.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's the point of all this?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.24,0:08:24.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's no point.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.99,0:08:27.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm doing it because I can. That's all there is to it.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.26,0:08:31.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What will come of this?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.63,0:08:33.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nothing at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.64,0:08:37.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She'll die and I'll burn out.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.07,0:08:38.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The end.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.15,0:08:40.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's all.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.78,0:08:44.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is that everything you desire?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.52,0:08:49.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Of course! What else could I wish for?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.98,0:08:52.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And what about you guys?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.49,0:08:54.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What have you accomplished while you've been alive?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.69,0:08:56.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What'll be left after you die?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.75,0:08:58.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nothing at all!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.26,0:09:02.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And just like that, everyone dies like pieces of trash!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.30,0:09:03.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Correct.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.51,0:09:06.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And that will also apply to you one day.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.47,0:09:11.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You'll have no proof of your existence nor a meaning in life...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.50,0:09:12.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...and die.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.92,0:09:14.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Quit joking around.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.79,0:09:16.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't compare me with you guys.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.20,0:09:23.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm the almighty Phantom!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.75,0:09:38.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've finally found the thing I'm better at than everyone else.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.33,0:09:41.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I found a way of life that people can't look down upon.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.67,0:09:48.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is all I am...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.76,0:09:53.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What I do is to take away and destroy.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.45,0:09:59.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't want to have it done to me anymore...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.62,0:10:49.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I thought you'd be here.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.30,0:10:53.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"I think this is the best choice."
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.94,0:10:55.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you really believe that?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.96,0:10:56.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.32,0:10:58.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You can't kill Cal.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.94,0:11:01.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, I can and I will.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.80,0:11:06.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll bear all her anger and sadness.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.80,0:11:14.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll be the saddest person in this world when she dies.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.23,0:11:16.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can mourn for her.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.54,0:11:19.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So let me kill her.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.07,0:11:23.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, you'll lose for sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.53,0:11:26.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll never let myself lose you.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.95,0:11:27.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Elen...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.94,0:11:30.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're the only one who can't do that.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.41,0:11:33.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Because you're gentle.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.44,0:11:37.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Because you won't be able to kill her.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.26,0:11:41.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll stay, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.05,0:11:44.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The two of us will definitely be able to defeat her.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.53,0:11:45.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You have to understand this!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.93,0:11:47.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is the seed I've sown!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.76,0:11:52.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If I don't settle this here, I'll always be bound by my past.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.46,0:11:55.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I won't be able to free myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.64,0:11:57.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Elen, leave first!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.38,0:12:00.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll come right after!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.00,0:12:02.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where can I go without you?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.04,0:12:06.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't even know where I came from...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.62,0:12:10.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't even have any memories!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.34,0:12:19.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What should I do to free myself?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.38,0:12:22.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What good is freedom built on the deaths of others?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.43,0:12:31.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tell me! Please!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.85,0:12:45.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go find it together.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.94,0:12:50.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll definitely return to your side to fulfill that promise.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.34,0:12:52.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Reiji...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.77,0:13:31.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Elen won't be coming.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.15,0:13:34.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why are you here?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.00,0:13:36.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is my duty.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.77,0:13:40.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,To protect that girl?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.73,0:13:42.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, Cal.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.01,0:13:47.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,To kill you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.51,0:13:51.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've sacrificed countless people up until now.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.84,0:13:57.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've tricked countless people,\Nused them and killed them in the end.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.96,0:14:00.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just for the sake of staying alive.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.76,0:14:03.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You've got quite the nerve...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.01,0:14:06.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're right, Cal.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.58,0:14:08.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Your anger represents justice.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.02,0:14:10.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You don't need to bring this to court.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.72,0:14:13.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just use your gun to bring judgment upon me.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.21,0:14:17.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Not by anyone else, but by yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.35,0:14:20.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you're stronger than me,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.42,0:14:24.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,then I'll be punished.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.45,0:14:27.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just the way I want it.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.93,0:14:50.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I won't let you interfere.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.45,0:14:51.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Get her!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.48,0:15:02.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you really want to have a match, then this is the perfect choice.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.41,0:15:03.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.63,0:15:05.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You still remember?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.78,0:15:09.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is our karma.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.54,0:15:11.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My guidepost up until now.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.39,0:15:17.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This thing always reminds me of who to hate and who to kill.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.34,0:15:27.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A duel.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.99,0:15:29.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When this song ends, we shoot.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.29,0:15:31.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.16,0:15:36.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're the only one...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.66,0:15:41.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...who is still alive after hearing this song, Reiji.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.16,0:16:49.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What? Did you fall asleep?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.08,0:16:54.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I had a dream about back when we were in Los Angeles.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.18,0:16:56.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What kind of dream?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.83,0:17:05.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What would've happened if we hadn't seen each other after the place got blown up?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.96,0:17:08.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's so stupid!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.55,0:17:11.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As if you'd make a stupid mistake like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.48,0:17:14.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That would never happen.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.59,0:17:17.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's no way we'll be separated.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.63,0:17:21.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If that really happened, I would go look for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.43,0:17:23.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even to the ends of the Earth...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.17,0:17:27.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's impossible.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.24,0:17:32.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm a hopeless idiot.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.54,0:17:37.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why am I thinking of such things?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.15,0:17:44.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It might not be so bad to think about things from time to time.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.79,0:17:49.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It might not be so bad...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.15,0:17:55.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,At least something like that can happen in a dream...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.16,0:18:11.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is this where Judy Devens passed away?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.20,0:18:21.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why are you so strong?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.54,0:18:26.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is this only way I can answer you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.68,0:18:30.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.84,0:18:38.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then I can still have you all to myself at the end?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.38,0:18:41.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's great...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.45,0:18:46.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't need anything else...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.68,0:18:51.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you have to sacrifice yourself for such things?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.90,0:18:55.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you mean by "such things"?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.66,0:18:59.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is there something better?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.30,0:19:08.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I think we had other ways to live our lives.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.52,0:19:14.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If we had met some other way, we might have been able to live happily ever after.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.84,0:19:15.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.94,0:19:21.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We just messed up somewhere, that's all...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.69,0:19:23.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That has to be it.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.83,0:19:30.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm glad I met you.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.36,0:19:33.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.88,0:19:35.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...satisfied...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.83,0:19:39.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...and happy...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.69,0:19:41.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Cal!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.73,0:19:58.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Cal...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.30,0:20:02.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,CAL!!!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.21,0:20:25.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Phantom, you monster!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.62,0:20:35.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I really don't understand this.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.50,0:20:41.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mr. Shiga, I thought you were smarter than this.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.43,0:20:45.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why didn't you just leave it to us?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.17,0:20:47.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You bastard!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.70,0:20:50.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You've been watching this whole time?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.67,0:20:53.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's time for the final act.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.09,0:20:56.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's no place in the cast for you unrefined stage props.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.87,0:21:01.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you want to stay, then please do so.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.94,0:21:09.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please feel privileged to be able to see my best work.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.19,0:21:13.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The concerto of the strongest ghosts.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.02,0:21:18.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now then, who will respond to the curtain call?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.79,0:21:36.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I will kill.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.89,0:21:43.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I will kill in order to live.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.31,0:21:52.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We are...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.92,0:21:55.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...ghosts that cannot exist anywhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.95,0:21:59.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We are phantoms with no identity.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.96,0:23:28.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In my wrongful life where I couldn't fulfill any promises,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.18,0:23:32.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,there is still one promise I want to fulfill.
